Eezy Coin (EZC)
The effortless digital currency empowering people, creators, and communities worldwide.
Welcome to Eezy Coin
Eezy Coin (EZC) represents the next step in accessible, decentralized finance. Designed to be fast, secure, and community-driven, EZC makes digital payments as easy as sending a text.
Our mission is to simplify blockchain technology so anyone—from seasoned investors to new users—can participate in the crypto revolution without barriers or confusion.
Get EZC Now
Technical Overview
	•	Blockchain: Eezy Network (Layer-1, EVM-compatible)
	•	Consensus: Hybrid Proof-of-Stake (PoS) + Delegated Governance
	•	Smart Contracts: Written in Solidity and audited by community reviewers
	•	Average Block Time: 2.5 seconds
	•	Transaction Fee: Less than $0.001 per tx
EZC utilizes advanced cryptography and energy-efficient consensus to ensure sustainability and scalability while maintaining decentralization.
Tokenomics
	•	Total Supply: 1,000,000,000 EZC
	•	Circulating Supply: 600,000,000 EZC
	•	Reserve Fund: 10% (locked 12 months)
	•	Community Rewards: 15%
	•	Development Fund: 10%
	•	Team & Advisors: 5% (vesting 24 months)
Transparency is a cornerstone of the EZC ecosystem. Token movements are traceable on-chain via the EezyScan Explorer.
Ecosystem & Use Cases
Eezy Coin fuels an expanding ecosystem of apps and partnerships, including:
	•	Peer-to-peer instant payments
	•	Tipping systems for creators and streamers
	•	Decentralized marketplaces
	•	Play-to-earn integrations
	•	Charity donations with 0% platform fees
Our motto: "Make crypto eezy, fun, and for everyone."
Roadmap
	1	Q1 2026: Launch testnet, community governance alpha
	2	Q2 2026: Mainnet release, first DEX listing
	3	Q3 2026: Mobile wallet, NFT integrations
	4	Q4 2026: DAO activation, global community events
Team & Community
Behind Eezy Coin is a group of developers, designers, and enthusiasts united by a simple belief: crypto should be inclusive, not intimidating. We host online AMAs, hackathons, and local meetups (like the one shown above) to keep the energy authentic.
Join our growing network on Discord, X (Twitter), and Reddit — or start your own Eezy crew.
How to Get EZC
	1	Install a crypto wallet (e.g., MetaMask or Eezy Wallet).
	2	Add the Eezy Network RPC (details below).
	3	Purchase EZC on EezySwap or supported exchanges.
Network Name: Eezy Mainnet
RPC URL: https://rpc.eezycoin.net
Chain ID: 2026
Symbol: EZC
Explorer: https://scan.eezycoin.net
Security & Compliance
All contracts are verified and open source. EZC supports KYC-compliant business integrations, while maintaining user privacy and non-custodial wallets for individuals.
Regular audits ensure long-term stability and trustworthiness of the protocol.
